-- Italy police seize 15 million euros at Merrill Lynch in fraud probe
-- 
-- Thu Oct 3, 2013 5:49am EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2013/10/03/us-italy-merrilllynch-idUSBRE9920AR20131003

 

 ROME  (Reuters) - Italy's financial police said on Thursday they had seized 15 million euros from Merrill Lynch ( BAC.N ) in Milan as part of a probe into alleged fraud against the city council of Verona. 
 The seizure was ordered by Verona prosecutors, a police spokesman said. Merrill Lynch declined to comment. (Reporting by  Antonella Cinelli , editing by Silvia Aloisi)